company_name: SEMCOM GESELLSCHAFT ZUR ERZEUGUNG UND KONTROLLE VON SAATGUT MBH
information: The company SEMCOM GESELLSCHAFT ZUR ERZEUGUNG UND KONTROLLE VON SAATGUT MBH, is a Service Provider, founded in 1990, which operates in the Bedding plants, bulbs and seeds industry. It is based in Meßdorf, Germany.
